#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Tips for Success<br/><br/></span></strong>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Tips til succes<br/><br/></span></strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Accounting</strong>: Automate invoices, reconcile payments, and "
"track profitability per tour type"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Bogføring</strong>: Automatisér fakturaer, afstem betalinger, og "
"følg rentabiliteten for hver turtype"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Activate the multilingual website setting to localize your website "
"to international audiences.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Aktivér flersproget funktionalitet for at tilpasse dit websted til "
"besøgende fra hele verden.</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"<strong>Antwerp</strong> dazzles with its fashion-forward spirit and rich "
"artistic heritage. Explore the legacy of Rubens, marvel at the gothic "
"Cathedral of Our Lady, and stroll through the dynamic streets of this port "
"city where tradition meets modern creativity."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Antwerpen</strong> byder på en unik kombination af mode og kunst. "
"Oplev Rubens’ mesterværker, gå på opdagelse i den gotiske "
"Liebfrauenkathedrale, og nyd stemningen i de livlige gader, hvor historie "
"møder moderne kreativitet."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Appointments</strong>: Allow customers to book private tours based "
"on availability and language preferences."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Aftaler</strong>: Giv kunderne mulighed for at booke private guidede "
"ture efter tilgængelighed og sprogpræferencer."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Apps &amp; What They Do:</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Apps, og hvad de kan:</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"<strong>Brussels</strong>, the heart of Europe, welcomes you with grand "
"architecture, cobblestone streets, and a vibrant atmosphere. From the "
"opulent Grand Place to the surreal world of Magritte, this city is a must-"
"see for culture lovers and history buffs alike."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Brussels</strong>, Europas hjerte, byder dig velkommen med storslået "
"arkitektur, brostensbelagte gader og en livlig atmosfære. Fra den overdådige "
"Grand Place til Magrittes surrealistiske univers er byen et must for både "
"kultur- og historieinteresserede."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create services</strong> for each destination &amp; language pair"
msgstr "<strong>Opret tjenester</strong> for hvert mål og hvert sprogpar"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create visually rich pages</strong> with images, videos, and tour "
"descriptions"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Opret visuelt tiltalende sider</strong> med billeder, videoer og "
"beskrivelser af ture"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Customers book online</strong> and receive <strong>automated "
"reminders</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Kunder booker online</strong>, og modtag <strong>automatiserede "
"påmindelser</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Customize layouts easily</strong> using drag-and-drop editor"
msgstr "<strong>Tilpas layouts nemt</strong> med træk og slip-editoren"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Dashboards</strong>: Visualize your KPIs—bookings per guide, top-"
"selling tours, revenue trends"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Dashboards</strong>: Visualisér dine KPI’er – bookinger pr. "
"rejseleder, mest populære ture og udviklingen i omsætningen"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Define each tour</strong> as an event with time slots and capacities"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Definér hver tur</strong> som en begivenhed med tidsrum og "
"deltagerkapacitet"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Define guide availability</strong> per service"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Definér, hvornår vejledningen er tilgængelig</strong> for hver "
"tjenesteydelse"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Digital tickets with QR codes</strong> for easy on-site check-in"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Digitale billetter med QR-koder</strong> til nem indtjekning på "
"stedet"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Enable online booking &amp; payment</strong>, no manual follow-up "
"needed"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Aktivér online booking og betaling</strong>, uden behov for manuel "
"opfølgning"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Events</strong>: Set up group tours with schedules and manage "
"bookings and attendance."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Arrangementer</strong>: Planlæg grupperejser med tidsplaner, og "
"håndtér både bookinger og tilstedeværelse."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"<strong>Ghent</strong> enchants with medieval splendor and a youthful "
"energy. Discover castles, canals, and hidden alleyways as you uncover the "
"soul of a city where past and present coexist in perfect harmony."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Gent</strong> charmerer med historisk pragt og livlig energi. "
"Udforsk slotte, kanaler og hemmelige gyder, og mærk byens sjæl, hvor fortid "
"og nutid mødes."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
msgid ""
"<strong>Ghent</strong> is the kind of city that sneaks up on you — and "
"steals your heart. A vibrant mix of gothic spires, canalside charm, artistic"
" rebellion, and youthful energy, Ghent is one of Belgium’s best-kept "
"secrets… though the word is definitely getting out."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Gent</strong> er en by, man først lægger mærke til på afstand, men "
"hurtigt bliver forelsket i. Med sin livlige blanding af gotiske tårne, "
"charmerende kanaler, kunstnerisk oprør og ungdommelig energi er Gent en af "
"Belgiens bedst bevarede hemmeligheder – selvom rygtet stille og roligt "
"breder sig."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Handle walk-in traffic</strong> efficiently with synced stock"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Effektiv håndtering af løbende kundeservice</strong> med "
"synkroniseret lagerbeholdning"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid "<strong>Included</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Inkluderet</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Integrate booking buttons</strong> directly with group or private "
"tour modules"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Integrer bookingknapper</strong> direkte i gruppe- eller "
"privaturtmoduler"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3841
msgid "<strong>Join Our Guided Group Tours — Discover More Together</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Tag med på vores guidede grupperejser – oplev mere i "
"fællesskab</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"<strong>Namur</strong>, nestled at the confluence of the Meuse and Sambre "
"rivers, invites you to slow down and savor the beauty of Wallonia. Its "
"imposing citadel, relaxed charm, and panoramic views make it a serene yet "
"fascinating stop on your Belgian adventure."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Namur</strong>, der ligger ved sammenløbet af Maas og Sambre, "
"inviterer dig til at tage dig tid til at nyde Walloniens skønhed. Den "
"imponerende citadel, byens afslappede charme og de panoramiske udsigter gør "
"Namur til et roligt, men fascinerende stop på din rejse gennem Belgien."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid "<strong>Not included</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Ikke inkluderet</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Open POS session</strong> and view tour availabilities"
msgstr "<strong>Åbn POS-sessionen</strong>, og se, hvilke ture er tilgængelige"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Optimize SEO</strong> to attract tourists searching online"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Optimér din søgemaskineoptimering</strong> for at tiltrække turister "
"via onlinesøgninger"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid "<strong>Our offering</strong><br>"
msgstr "<strong>Vores tilbud</strong><br>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Point of Sale</strong>: Sell tickets in person, print receipts, and "
"manage real-time tour availabilities."
msgstr ""
"<strong>POS</strong>: Sælg billetter personligt, udskriv kvitteringer og "
"administrér ledige ture i realtid."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Print receipts</strong> with booking details"
msgstr "<strong>Udkriv kvitteringer</strong> med alle reservationsoplysninger"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Recruitment</strong>: Manage applications and onboarding for new "
"tour guides"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Rekruttering</strong>: Håndtér ansøgninger og onboarding for nye "
"rejseledere"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Regularly update website content</strong> with new tours, seasonal "
"offerings, and high-quality visuals"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Opdatér løbende din hjemmeside</strong> med nye ture, sæsontilbud og "
"billeder i høj kvalitet"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Reminders &amp; confirmation emails</strong> reduce no-shows"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Påmindelses- og bekræftelsesmails</strong> mindsker antallet af "
"udeblivelser"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Sell remaining spots</strong> for today’s tours or future ones"
msgstr "<strong>Sælg de ledige pladser</strong> på dagens eller kommende ture"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Social Marketing</strong>: Schedule and post on social media to "
"boost tour visibility"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Markedsføring på sociale medier</strong>: Planlæg og del indlæg på "
"sociale medier for at øge synligheden af dine ture"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Surveys</strong>: Gather guest feedback after each tour to "
"continuously improve"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Spørgeundersøgelser</strong>: Indsaml gæsternes feedback efter hver "
"tur for løbende at forbedre oplevelsen"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Track attendance live</strong> from a mobile device or the "
"attendances app"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Hold øje med tilstedeværelse i realtid</strong> via mobil eller "
"Tilstedeværelsesappen"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Train staff</strong> on using POS for quick ticketing"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Træn personalet</strong> i kassesystemet, så de hurtigt kan udstede "
"billetter"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Use QR check-ins</strong> to save time and reduce human error"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Brug QR-registreringer</strong> for at spare tid og minimere fejl"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Use automated emails</strong> to remind customers of their upcoming "
