#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the Events app to manage recurring group tours, online bookings, and "
"attendee tracking."
msgstr ""
"Administrér tilbagevendende grupperejser, onlinebookinger og "
"deltageropfølgning med Arrangementerappen."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.homepage
msgid ""
"Using flexible planning, we deliver tailored travel solutions that adapt "
"quickly to your preferences and feedback."
msgstr ""
"Med fleksibel planlægning tilbyder vi skræddersyede rejseløsninger, der "
"hurtigt kan tilpasses dine ønsker og din feedback."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3841
msgid ""
"Walk alongside fellow travelers as our passionate guides bring each city to "
"life — from medieval alleyways and majestic cathedrals to modern "
"neighborhoods full of local flavor. Our groups are <strong>small enough to "
"stay personal</strong>, but <strong>big enough to share laughs and "
"moments</strong> you'll remember long after the tour ends."
msgstr ""
"Ledsag dine medrejsende, mens vores engagerede rejseledere bringer hver by "
"til live – fra middelalderlige gader og majestætiske katedraler til moderne "
"kvarterer fyldt med lokal atmosfære. Vores grupper er <strong>små nok til at "
"bevare den personlige</strong> kontakt, men <strong>store nok til at dele "
"grin og øjeblikke</strong>, du vil huske længe efter rejsen."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3836
msgid ""
"We are a team of passionate people whose goal is to improve everyone's life "
"through disruptive products. We build great products to solve your business "
"problems. Our products are designed for small to medium size companies "
"willing to optimize their performance."
msgstr ""
"Vi er et team af passionerede mennesker, der stræber efter at forbedre alles "
"liv med nyskabende produkter. Vi skaber løsninger, der hjælper dig med at "
"løse dine forretningsudfordringer. Vores produkter er designet til små og "
"mellemstore virksomheder, der ønsker at optimere deres ydeevne."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.homepage
msgid ""
"We focus on crafting personalized itineraries, ensuring memorable and high-"
"quality travel experiences that meet your expectations."
msgstr ""
"Vi skaber individuelle rejseplaner, der giver dig uforglemmelige og "
"eksklusive oplevelser, skræddersyet til dine forventninger."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid ""
"We offer a 30-day return policy for all products. Items must be in their "
"original condition, unused, and include the receipt or proof of purchase. "
"Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days of receiving the returned "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Vi tilbyder 30-dages returret på alle produkter. Varerne skal returneres i "
"deres originale emballage, være ubrugte og vedlægges kvittering eller "
"købsbevis. Refusioner behandles inden for 5–7 hverdage efter modtagelse af "
"den returnerede vare."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.homepage
msgid ""
"We prioritize safety measures at every stage, ensuring your travel "
"experience is secure and worry-free."
msgstr ""
"Vi prioriterer sikkerheden i alle faser, så du kan nyde en tryg og "
"bekymringsfri rejseoplevelse."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "Website Documentation"
msgstr "Dokumentation til Hjemmeside"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "Website 🌐"
msgstr "Hjemmeside 🌐"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid ""
"Welcome to <strong>Antwerp</strong>, Belgium’s bold, bustling port city "
"where <strong>diamonds, design, and centuries of history</strong> sparkle "
"side by side. As the country’s fashion capital and one of Europe’s most "
"important trading hubs, Antwerp is a city that has always done things its "
"own way — with flair, creativity, and confidence."
msgstr ""
"Velkommen til <strong>Antwerpen</strong>, Belgiens dynamiske havneby, hvor "
"<strong>diamanter, design og århundredgammel historie</strong> skinner side "
"om side. Som landets modehovedstad og et af Europas vigtigste "
"handelsknudepunkter er Antwerpen en by, der altid har fulgt sine egne veje – "
"med flair, kreativitet og selvsikkerhed."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
msgid ""
"Welcome to <strong>Brussels</strong>, the capital not only of Belgium, but "
"of Europe itself. A city where history, politics, art, and chocolate all "
"collide in a vibrant, multicultural atmosphere. With its iconic landmarks, "
"whimsical architecture, grand squares, and quirky corners, Brussels is full "
"of surprises — and there’s no better way to experience it all than from the "
"comfort of a guided bus tour."
msgstr ""
"Velkommen til <strong>Bruxelles</strong>, ikke blot Belgien, men Europas "
"hovedstad. Her mødes historie, politik, kunst og chokolade i en livlig, "
"multikulturel atmosfære. Med ikoniske seværdigheder, finurlig arkitektur, "
"store pladser og charmerende hjørner er Bruxelles fuld af overraskelser – og "
"den bedste måde at opleve det hele på er fra en komfortabel guidet bustur."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model:product.public.category,name:guided_tours.product_public_category_6
msgid "Wellness"
msgstr "Wellness"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid ""
"We’re committed to providing prompt and effective solutions to ensure your "
"satisfaction."
msgstr ""
"Vi bestræber os på at tilbyde hurtige og effektive løsninger for at sikre "
"os, at du er glad og tilfreds."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"Whether you're a first-time visitor or rediscovering Belgium, our guided "
"tours offer insider stories, hidden gems, and unforgettable moments."
msgstr ""
"Uanset om det er dit første besøg, eller du ønsker at genopdage Belgien, "
"byder vores guidede ture på insiderhistorier, skjulte skatte og "
"uforglemmelige øjeblikke."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid ""
"Whether you're a history lover, an art enthusiast, a curious traveler, or "
"just here for the vibes, <strong>Antwerp will impress you — and our bus tour"
" makes sure you experience it all, effortlessly.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Uanset om du er historieinteresseret, kunstelsker, nysgerrig rejsende eller "
"bare vil nyde byens atmosfære, vil <strong>Antwerpen imponere – og vores "
"bustur sørger for, at du kan opleve det hele uden besvær.</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
msgid ""
"Whether you're enchanted by history, drawn to culture, or just here to soak "
"in the vibe (and maybe a local beer), this tour is the ideal way to get "
"oriented and inspired. <strong>Ghent is a city of stories — and we can’t "
"wait to tell you some.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Uanset om du er historieinteresseret, fascineres af kultur eller blot vil "
"nyde atmosfæren (og måske smage en lokal øl), er denne tur den ideelle måde "
"at orientere dig på og lade dig inspirere. <strong>Gent er en by fuld af "
"historier – og vi glæder os til at dele nogle af dem med dig.</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
msgid ""
"Whether you're here for the first time or rediscovering the capital through "
"new eyes, this tour offers the perfect balance of comfort, culture, and "
"curiosity. <strong>Brussels is complex, beautiful, and alive — let us show "
"you its heart.<br><br></strong>"
msgstr ""
"Uanset om det er dit første besøg, eller du vil genopdage hovedstaden med "
"friske øjne, tilbyder denne tur den perfekte balance mellem komfort, kultur "
"og nysgerrighed. Bruxelles er kompleks, smuk og livlig – og vi inviterer dig "
"til at opleve byens hjerte.<br><br></strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.homepage
msgid "Why book with us"
msgstr "Derfor skal du booke hos os"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid ""
"With expert commentary from a passionate guide, you’ll hear stories of "
"Rubens and rock stars, shipping magnates and tailors, chocolatiers and "
"revolutionaries. From the elegant Meir shopping street to the futuristic "
"Port House, from hidden alleyways to grand plazas — this tour covers the "
"full spectrum of Antwerp’s unique identity."
msgstr ""
"Med kyndige forklaringer fra en engageret rejseleder får du historier om "
"Rubens og rockstjerner, rederier og skræddere, chokoladeproducenter og "
"revolutionære. Fra den elegante shoppinggade Meir til det futuristiske Port "
"House, fra skjulte gyder til storslåede pladser – denne tur viser hele "
"spektret af Antwerpens unikke identitet."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or explore more features?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller udforske flere funktioner?"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can choose to allow customers to book resources (see demo data) or "
"users, which is integrated into the planning app. Using resources allows for"
" more flexibility (sharing resources, linking resources to each other for "
"larger groups)."
msgstr ""
"Du kan lade kunder reservere ressourcer (se demodata) eller brugere direkte "
"i planlægningsappen. Ressourcehåndtering giver større fleksibilitet, f.eks. "
"til deling eller sammensætning af større grupper."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid ""
"You can reach our customer support team by emailing "
"info@yourcompany.example.com, calling +1 555-555-5556, or using the live "
"chat on our website. Our dedicated team is available 24/7 to assist with any"
" inquiries or issues."
msgstr ""
"Du kan få kontakt til vores kundesupport ved at skrive til dem på "
"info@dinvirksomhed.eksempel.com, ringe til +1 555-555-5556 eller bruge "
"livechatten på vores hjemmeside. Vores dedikerede team står klar til at "
"hjælpe dig og besvare dine spørgsmål døgnet rundt."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "You can still do it by upgrading your package in Apps."
msgstr "Du kan fortsat gøre dette ved at opdatere din pakke via Apps."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid ""
"You'll travel in style aboard a comfortable, air-conditioned coach, with "
"plenty of opportunities to stop, snap photos, and soak up the atmosphere. "
"And yes — we’ll give you a taste of something local on board. Think waffles,"
" pralines, or maybe a fine Antwerpse Handje."
msgstr ""
"Rejs med stil i en komfortabel, klimatiseret turistbus, med masser af "
"muligheder for stop, billeder og at nyde stemningen. Og ja – vi forkæler dig "
"med en lokal specialitet, f.eks. vafler, chokolade eller måske en lækker "
"Antwerpse Handje."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3836
msgid "hello@mycompany.com"
msgstr "hej@minvirksomhed.dk"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
msgid "🚌 Discover Namur: Belgium’s Hidden Gem"
msgstr "🚌 Oplev Namur: Belgiens skjulte perle"
